Cryptostore
===========

| |License|
| |Python|
| |PyPi|

A storage engine for crypto market data. You supply the exchanges, data
type (trade, book, etc), and trading pairs you're interested in and
Cryptostore does the rest!

Stores data to:

-  Parquet
-  Arctic

Planned features
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

-  [x] Dynamic/Reloadable Config
-  [x] Parquet support
-  [x] Arctic support
-  [ ] Parquet files in S3/GC
-  [ ] Missing data detection and correction (for exchanges that support
   historical data, typically only trade data)

